      "comment": "SLICK ROCKET (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (25.65) in a Grade 4/5 at Shepparton. Key runner on his best form. UNDERCOVER GUY (7) has a strong winning strike-rate here having won two of four starts. Scored by a neck last time (28.38) in a Grade 5 over 500m at this track. Among the main chances. ATHENS AURA (8) failed to come into contention last start at this track, but prior to that won by 1.3 lengths at this track (28.74) beating Lizard Country in a Grade 5 on February 18. The form from her last run stacks up well. Worth another chance. MORAINE DYLAN (4) placed last time (34.93) at The Meadows in a Grade 4/5, finishing third and beaten 4 lengths. Already a winner from this draw.",
